it.unibo.ai.didattica.competition.tablut.AI

Class AlphaBetaSearch

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unibo.ai.didattica.competition.tablut.AI.AlphaBetaSearch

  • public class AlphaBetaSearch
extends java.lang.Object
    Implements an iterative Minimax search with alpha-beta pruning which at every iteration increase the depth of the search in order to have an aprroximation of all the lower depth values in case of timeout and action ordering. Maximal computation time is specified in seconds.
    Author:
    Arcangelo Alberico

    • Method Detail

      • makeDecision

        public Action makeDecision(State state)
        Execute the algorithm on the passed state in order to return the best action to be perfomed. It shuffles any time the allowed actions in order to have better perfomance. In case of the white player the king's actions are placed at the beginning of the array in order to be evaluated first.
        Parameters:
        state - state from which calculate the action according the algorithm
        Returns:
        the action to be performed
